---
/* "MADiE Tool Overview" section */
---
<section class="overview" aria-label="MADiE Tool Overview">
  <div class="container overview__inner">
    <div class="overview__content">
      <h2 class="overview__heading">MADiE Tool Overview</h2>
      <p class="overview__text">
        MADiE is a software tool that redefines the electronic Clinical Quality Measure
        (i.e., eCQM, measure) development and testing process by making it a
        self-contained process that includes dynamic authoring and testing within a single
        application.
      </p>
      <p class="overview__text">
        The tool provides the capability to author and test eCQMs in both the Quality
        Data Model (QDM) and Fast Healthcare Interoperability Resources (FHIR) models.
        MADiE also allows users to export the measures and test cases in different formats,
        depending on the selected model.
      </p>
      <a href="/training-resources" class="btn btn-primary">
        Learn more in Training & Resources
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="overview__image-wrapper">
      <img
        src="/images/female-doctor.png"
        alt="Doctor working at computer"
        class="overview__image"
        width="352"
        height="440"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .overview {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }
  .overview__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .overview__heading {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary-darker);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .overview__text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-base-dark);
  }
  .overview__image-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .overview__image {
    border-radius: 12px;
    object-fit: cover;
    max-height: 440px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .overview__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .overview__image-wrapper {
      order: -1;
    }
    .overview {
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
    }
  }
</style>
